2:T70d,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is AI Writer better than Postwise?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. AI Writer scores 5.0 overall while Postwise scores 6.0. AI Writer is best for research articles and cited content, while Postwise excels for Twitter/X threads and LinkedIn posts."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, AI Writer or Postwise?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"AI Writer starts at $29/mo and Postwise starts at $29/mo.   Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from AI Writer to Postwise?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both AI Writer and Postwise support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about AI Writer vs Postwise?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, AI Writer holds an overall rating of 5/10 and an ease of use score of 5/10. Postwise has an overall rating of 6/10 and ease of use score of 8/10. Users praise AI Writer for auto-generates citations and sources and Postwise for purpose-built for twitter/x and linkedin."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, AI Writer or Postwise?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Postwise for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, AI Writer remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize auto-generates citations and sources. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"classN