c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both AI Writer and Postwise share a solid foundation of core features including . Where AI Writer pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Long Form and Seo Tools and Api Access, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Postwise uniquely offers Short Form and Templates and Tone Control, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, AI Writer holds an overall score of 5/10 and an ease of use score of 5/10, while Postwise scores 6/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both platforms start at similar price points ($29/mo). Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
