10:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. AI Writer is best suited for research articles, cited content, SEO writing, fact based content, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Postwise, meanwhile, shines for Twitter/X threads, LinkedIn posts, social media growth, personal branding, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2015, AI Writer describes itself as \"AI article writer that cites sources and verifies claims.\" Postwise, established in 2022, positions itself as \"AI ghostwriter for Twitter/X and LinkedIn content.\" With 7 years between them, AI Writer brings the maturity and proven track record of a veteran platform, while Postwise offers the fresh perspective and modern architecture of a newer entrant."}]]}]
11:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Postwise** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (6.0 vs 5.0). However, this does not mean AI Writer is a poor choice — far from it. AI Writer excels in its own right, particularly for research articles and cited content.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value purpose-built for twitter/x and linkedin, go with Postwise. If auto-generates citations and sources matters more to you, AI Writer is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
